齊合作嘅同伴，同伴之間要互相尊重，唔好咁易中咗政府同三毛嘅分化計<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今次唔排除有三毛混入開假膠post / 推膠post，之前嗰啲垃圾post我當一時on9，如果今日起（9/7/2019）再發現有任何人開膠post，一律當三毛處理</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a97707e57e76c8e651a28dfb4d84b7de0e61d06","tid":1297690,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:58:51.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">「有冇聽過狼來了?」\n「真係要人冇人出唔好問點解」\n「你哋害緊自己友」\n「垃圾小學雞」\n「你哋膠化緊成件事」\n「係咪以為自己好幽默?」\n「連登又變返兒登」\n「邊個再post我block邊個」\n「再有人開膠post就係鬼」</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7523259b75e4378bce40e419076cddd4565e8700","tid":1297690,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"痴撚線如果打緊仗<br />\n呢班仆街很撚定要拖去犬決"},{"pid":"8ecf303b11970b2d7d26e0917c815602684f07f9","tid":1297690,"uid":35373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7523259b75e4378bce40e419076cddd4565e8700","tid":1297690,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"痴撚線如果打緊仗<br />\n呢班仆街很撚定要拖去犬決"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2cce2939e5e18e5fde206fd4d4010424e84195","tid":1297690,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a017cd9bc3c7b0e04d8d11e52dd82eeacec00013","tid":1297690,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a8bca535023bfad966234fa50a340196fcabca9","tid":1297690,"uid":76382,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:28:25.000Z","msg":"如果下次再有呢啲情況<br />\n大家應該好似今晚咁盡快出post澄清<br />\n同夾手推上熱門 避免真係有人信出咗去<br />\n如果個個都block哂呢班人<br />\n下次就冇人知又有人玩膠架啦！！<br />\n記住依家多咗好多冇ac嘅人追連登post<br />\n你b